The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy profiles of Watson Laboratories, Inc.

's Pimecrolimus Cream, 1% to those of Valeant Pharmaceuticals North America LLC's Elidel(R) (pimecrolimus) Cream, 1%, and to demonstrate the superior efficacy of the two active creams over that of the placebo (Vehicle of test product), in the treatment of mild to moderate atopic dermatitis.

